OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHouseholds to be spared net
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fzero levy - Shapps         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Householders will not have to pay more 
OL,6, on their energy bills to fund hydrogen 
OL,7, production, Grant Shapps has indicated.
OL,9,FAn annual levy was expected to be      
OL,10,Fintroduced in 2025 to cover the cost   
OL,11,Fgap between producing low-carbon       
OL,12,Fhydrogen and polluting fossil fuels.   
OL,14,FBut, signalling a U-turn Mr Shapps said
OL,15,Fhe opposed a direct charge on the bills
OL,16,Fof energy consumers.                   
OL,18,FHe said: "I don't want to see people's 
OL,19,Fhousehold bills unnecessarily bashed by
OL,20,Fthis."                                 
